Genome-wide identification, evolution and expression analysis of bone 
morphogenetic protein (BMP) gene family in chinese soft-shell turtle (Pelodiscus 
sinensis).

Lei L(1)(2), Zhu J(1)(3), Chen C(1), Wang Y(1), Wu C(1), Qi M(4), Wang Y(1), Liu 
X(1), Hong X(1), Yu L(1), Chen H(1), Wei C(1), Liu Y(1), Li W(1), Zhu 
X(1)(2)(3).

Author information:
(1)Key Laboratory of Tropical and Subtropical Fishery Resources Application and 
